{"tid":277432,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"求救！女友屋企比家賊偷錢","createTime":"2017-06-09T14:47:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-14T14:52:57.000Z","uid":29959,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"252b792ad0650217448807d3dac85c255e7dcf0b","tid":277432,"uid":29959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T14:47:58.000Z","msg":"我女友同緊阿媽、細佬、阿爸(後父)一齊住<br />\n阿媽同阿爸關系一直唔好<br />\n成日只識洗錢，但又唔比家用<br />\n對阿媽唔好<br />\n但都一直忍住，唔離婚，太心軟，一離就好多野煩<br />\n細佬又未出生，讀緊中三<br />\n阿爸成日早出晚歸，唔知佢做咩<br />\n今日突然知道阿爸偷左阿媽張信用卡，借左成十萬<br />\n完全無能力還<br />\n諗過報警，但後果唔敢諗<br />\n因為驚發生淪常慘案<br />\n之前都同佢發生過爭執，佢去拎刀威脅<br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以比到建議點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n作為男友都唔識點做，無理由幫佢還，自己都冇咁多錢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"192eb653e034395a6ed8e686e1832af81a16bbbe","tid":277432,"uid":48358,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T14:49:50.000Z","msg":"做ptgf"},{"pid":"4df633a0a7ff6d4764777904c4b04c15b77ac499","tid":277432,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T14:50:36.000Z","msg":"一係你賣屎忽<br />\n一係叫你條女賣屎忽"},{"pid":"61e6d7f171019af96c7cd003b0579b9106867b75","tid":277432,"uid":29959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T14:51:03.000Z","msg":"認真呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea52c247383d7180e22c0fc3f5c7a1bdd311f2bb","tid":277432,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T14:52:15.000Z","msg":"我認真啊"},{"pid":"4c6bf60051a70bae11df3099d668d1d4b0a4dd22","tid":277432,"uid":90089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T14:53:39.000Z","msg":"揾社工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d5f97e380feaebd9f5034d344ff9d7c038a6bcd","tid":277432,"uid":96,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T14:54:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>揾社工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n社工都係報警撚 不如自己快快脆報好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dd9989dd26f7902876baf4d8d57750ea0f13c1f","tid":277432,"uid":66468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T14:54:36.000Z","msg":"如果係真，報警都分分鐘唔受理<br />\n揾社工又好似無乜約束力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n諗起《天水圍的夜與霧》"},{"pid":"59c383644f821ca384fe4b1578ef4c027fdf7ae9","tid":277432,"uid":29959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T14:55:33.000Z","msg":"點搞呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45c8838af8852b4f2c790e17d35c57bcdfc1dd2c","tid":277432,"uid":29959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T14:55:49.000Z","msg":"除左報驚係咪冇方法？"},{"pid":"4a144bbd1a82fc7bc0c973b5e91d83fe3a89a243","tid":277432,"uid":117868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T14:56:53.000Z","msg":"錯重點<br />\n細佬仲未出生就中三<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbe7b12f939991676419c98d1e2ff1d05c296c69","tid":277432,"uid":30745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T14:57:50.000Z","msg":"未出生就中生係唔係