":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T16:05:10.000Z","msg":"負皮係俾文盲樓豬嘅"},{"pid":"3886d4fc5ce27d69008eb772a07d5b5980c85d7f","tid":277432,"uid":34217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T16:12:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>叫你女友同老母先打去信用卡公司話比人盜用</blockquote><br />\n好似冇用<br />\n試過跌銀包發現即打去cut卡再去差館報失<br />\n月尾張單多左條2千幾蚊既數要照找</blockquote><br />\n咁係你問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6e70799caf106acf0882984d56974f22f9b3c8c","tid":277432,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T16:14:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我女友同緊阿媽、細佬、阿爸(後父)一齊住<br />\n阿媽同阿爸關系一直唔好<br />\n成日只識洗錢，但又唔比家用<br />\n對阿媽唔好<br />\n但都一直忍住，唔離婚，太心軟，一離就好多野煩<br />\n細佬又未<span style=\"color: red;\">出生</span>，讀緊中三<br />\n阿爸成日早出晚歸，唔知佢做咩<br />\n今日突然知道阿爸偷左阿媽張信用卡，借左成十萬<br />\n完全無能力還<br />\n諗過報警，但後果唔敢諗<br />\n因為驚發生淪常慘案<br />\n之前都同佢發生過爭執，佢去拎刀威脅<br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以比到建議點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n作為男友都唔識點做，無理由幫佢還，自己都冇咁多錢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n覺得好慘<br />\n但睇到呢個位又忍唔到笑<br />\n諗緊點樣未出世又讀到中三<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">出身</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實靜雞雞報警應該唔可行<br />\n始終調查期間又係住埋同一間屋<br />\n或者搵個地方<br />\n趁老豆出街<br />\n一家三口即搬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好畀佢知新地址同埋新聯絡方法<br />\n如果係盜用而又報警<br />\n證明到嘅話<br />\n可能唔需要還<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}